      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained luxury sport sedan that perfectly balances performance with daily usability. The exterior paint retains a deep, lustrous shine and has been regularly waxed; while there are a few minor stone chips on the leading edge of the hood consistent with highway driving, the body is straight and free of any major dents or scratches. Inside, the cabin is a pristine environment. The premium leather seats are supple with no cracks or bolster wear, and the genuine wood trim remains vibrant. All interior electronics\u2014including the navigation system, heated seats, and dual-zone climate control\u2014are fully operational. Mechanically, this car is turn-key. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule at authorized service centers, and I have a comprehensive folder of maintenance records to prove it. The engine runs smoothly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and the suspension remains tight and responsive. It recently passed a multi-point inspection and sits on tires with plenty of tread remaining. This is a smoke-free, garage-kept vehicle that offers a refined driving experience for its next owner.",
